  "text": "The RP was calculated according Prevost and Wilkinson [CITATION_1] : RP = ∑I b, where, I b represents how informative the locus is of the polymorphism. The I b can be translated into a 0-1 scale using the formula: I b = 1 − (2 × |0.5 -p|), where, p is the proportion of the genotypes showing the locus.",
